              {
                "name": "prompt",
                "value": "=You are a routing system. Return ONLY valid JSON. No markdown, no extra text.\n\nAvailable agents:\n{{ $json.agentList }}\n\nRecent context:\n{{ $json.recentMemory }}\n\nUser message: {{ $json.userMessage }}\n\nRouting rules:\n- If the message is \"פירוט\" or \"תן פירוט\" or \"פרט\" → action: chitchat\n- בקשה לכתיבת קוד, דיבאג, פונקציה, סקריפט → action: use_agent, agent_name: code_helper\n- Casual talk, greetings, small talk, questions about yourself, emotions, opinions, asking about agents list → action: chitchat\n- Task that matches an existing agent exactly → action: use_agent\n- Task with no matching agent → action: create_agent\n\nReturn ONLY:\n{\n  \"action\": \"chitchat\" or \"use_agent\" or \"create_agent\",\n  \"agent_name\": \"exact agent name if use_agent, null otherwise\"\n}"
              },
              {
                "name": "stream",
                "value": false
              }
            ]
          },
          "options": {}
        },
        "id": "5ef197f1-ce4f-4896-9036-4f2080e9084a",
